    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, entirely free from stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the premium leather still carries that distinct new-car aroma, with every bolster firm and every stitch intact. Every electronic component functions with factory-spec precision, and the cabin is whisper-quiet. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; the engine delivers power with surgical smoothness, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. All original documentation, a comprehensive service history, and both sets of keys are included. This isn't just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
