    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to be listing this absolute beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014it\u2019s been my pride and joy, and it drives like a total dream. If you're looking for something that's basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you're interested; I'd love to chat more about it!",
